title: Grateful Dead Live at Berkeley Community Theater on 1986-04-19
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Stagger Lee, Minglewood Blues, Friend Of The Devil, Cassidy, Big Railroad Blues, One More Saturday Night

Set 2

Crazy Fingers-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> The Other One-> China Doll-> Playin' In The Band-> Sugar Magnolia, E: The Mighty Quinn

Rex Benefit
